name: TEM MARKET
description: TEM Project Introduction TEM is building a next-generation Web3 peer-to-peer (P2P) digital asset marketplace. On TEM, users can trade, earn, and own across a wide range of assets — from NFTs and game items to tokens, vouchers, and software. Key features include: Decentralized P2P Trading – Direct transactions between users, powered by smart contracts. Trade-to-Earn (T2E) – Every trade generates rewards in $TEM tokens. Lucky Box System – Daily prize draws offering crypto, NFTs, gadgets, and more. Staking & Utility – $TEM can be staked for passive income, used for trading fees, or redeemed in ecosystem services. Global Accessibility – Borderless trading that’s fast, transparent, and secure. TEM isn’t just a trading platform — it’s a complete Web3 digital economy, designed to give power back to the users.
